{{!--
  Feature Grid Partial
  Displays feature categories with their features in a clean table grid.

  Expected context:
    - categories      {array}   Category objects from features.json. Each has:
                                  id, name, tagline?, features[]
    - stats           {object}  Stats object from features.json:
                                  totalCommands, apiEndpoints, webPages, commandGroups, modals
    - artifactTypes   {array}   Optional. ArtifactType objects from features.json.
                                When present, an "Artifact Types" table is appended.

  Handlebars helpers required by the build script:
    (none beyond built-in each/if)

  Project-specific display text (the "{{stats.X}}+ CLI commands" line) can be
  overridden by the build script by passing a preformatted `statsLine` string
  instead of the individual stat fields.
--}}
